source.name: Open Summonses - Active For-Hire-Vehicle (FHV) Owners
source.description: List of open summonses written against TLC-licensed vehicles. Only open summonses that have not yet been heard in court are shown – that means that the hearings have not happened and a final decision has not been made in these cases. File includes Vehicle License Number, Vehicle's Affiliated Base Number, Summons NNumber, Date Summons Issued, Charge and Disposition.
